cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image-text matching and semantic correspondence between vision and language. It could also belong to the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-category as it involves text processing. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with finding and correlating shared semantics in image and text. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Multimedia (cs.MM) are also possible sub-categories as the paper proposes a novel neural network architecture for image-text matching.
